[12/02/2017 19:19:38] <font color="#0000ff"></font>
[12/02/2017 19:19:38] <font color="#0000ff">(Aplausos)</font>
[12/02/2017 19:19:40] <font color="#ffff00">¡Qué detallazo!</font>
